strings.Value: [Pay 23 gold] "I'd like to spend the night here."
{n}An elderly barbarian waves his hand, inviting you to come closer.{/n} "Welcome, honored guest! Would you like to buy or sell anything?"

"Name's Dug. Was a hell of a fighter when I was younger, but truth, those years pass before you know it. The health, too." {n}The barbarian raises his hand, and you can see he only has two fingers left.{/n} "So now my job is equipment and provisions, along with a bit of trading from time to time."
{n}The aged barbarian gives you a hospitable nod.{/n}
